Problem is in this check:

`
 auto camera = Camera::getVisitingCamera();
 // Camera isn't null means in touch begin process, otherwise use _hittedByCamera instead.
 if (clippingParent->hitTest(pt, (camera ? camera : _hittedByCamera), nullptr))
`

`camera` is `null` outside of scene rendering `_hittedByCamera` is `null` outside of touching sequence. So `hitTest` will always return false.

